text_raw:
2. The 7th day of July 2021 is appointed as the day on which so much of the 
Data Sharing and Governance Act 2019 (No. 5 of 2019) as is not in operation 
(other than subsections (2) and (3) of section 6) comes into operation.

heading: 3. The 31st day of March 2022 is appointed as the day on which subsections
text_raw:
3. The 31st day of March 2022 is appointed as the day on which subsections 
(2) and (3) of section 6 of the Data Sharing and Governance Act 2019 come into 
operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

7 July, 2021. 

MICHAEL MCGRATH, 

Minister for Public Expenditure and Reform. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 13th July, 2021.
